====Signature Format====

SHRINCS signatures can exceed the 520-byte limit for stack elements. Therefore, the new tapscript version <code>0xC2</code> introduced in this BIP lifts the 520 byte limit on witness stack element sizes.

SHRINCS signatures may either use the stateful or the stateless path inside the key, and either is equally valid. Stateless SHRINCS signatures are very large, but always a constant size. Stateful SHRINCS signatures are much shorter, but are of variable size.


