* <s>Which opcodes should be redefined?</s> We should redefine OP_CHECKSIG et al with new tap leaf version
* <s>Are we adding CHECKSIGVERIFY or just CHECKSIG? How about CHECKSIGADD?</s> Not needed if redefining existing opcodes
